des:
I am John Holt, Realtor at Re/Max Advantage REALTORS in Searcy, Arkansas. I'll be sharing super cool new listings, tips for buying and selling that maybe nobody thinks about, home maintenance and random insights from a day's work, some love for all things music, and probably crazy stories from living with my precocious daughter. 
Join me and her in our daily joy and surprises on Instagram @rocknrollrealestate, Snapchat @rocknrollre, Twitter @RocknRollRealEstate, or on Facebook.
